high_descs: Take a few steps to the left to find the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife that is closest to the microwave.
Take the knife, turn around and go right to find the sink.
Place the knife in the left side of the sink, and turn the water on in the right side of the sink. Turn the water off, and pick up the knife.
Take the knife and take a step to the right.
Place the knife on the counter, right in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a knife in the sink then move it to the counter.

high_descs: Move to the left and face the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick the knife up from the counter.
Turn to the left and face the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the knife up out of the sink.
Move slightly to the right of the sink.
Set the knife down on the counter in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on the counter.

high_descs: Stand in front of the microwave.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Go to the sink on your left.
Wash the knife in the sink.
Move to the right side of the sink.
Put the knife on the counter in front of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed knife on the counter in front of the sink.
